creates a new reminder
```
!r new <expression> [message]
```
you can also create reminders with attachments
### Examples
creates a new reminder with durational expression
```
!r new 10h5m
```
creates a new reminder with hhmm expression
```
!r new 17:00
```
creates a new reminder with date expression
```
!r new 1.1.2024 happy new year!
```
creates a new reminder with time expression
```
!r new 8.11.2024-9:00 good morning and happy birthday!
```
creates a new reminder with custom message
```
!r new 10h5m clean up the room
```